Hello! This is William Griffin from Harmony Music School. How can I assist you today?

Hi William! My name is Karen King. I'm interested in learning more about your privacy policies.

Nice to meet you, Karen! I'd be happy to help. To ensure I provide the most relevant information, could you please give me your email address?

Sure, my email is karen.king@example.com.

Thank you, Karen. And could you also provide your phone number, just in case we need to contact you directly with any updates?

Of course, my phone number is five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Great, I've got that noted down. At Harmony Music School, we take privacy seriously and ensure all personal information is securely stored and never shared without your consent.

That sounds reassuring. Thank you for explaining, William.

You're very welcome, Karen. If you have any other questions, feel free to ask.

No more questions from my side. Thank you for your help!

Thank you for your time, Karen. Have a wonderful day!
